    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Clean, honest classic in good overall condition and a great choice for someone who wants a vintage car they can enjoy right away. It presents nicely with solid driver-quality cosmetics, a tidy appearance, and the kind of character that makes these cars so appealing. Not a concours example, but a well-kept, good-condition driver with plenty of charm and a strong value in today\u2019s market.",
