    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an affordable price point. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who values low upfront cost and opportunity over perfection. A practical option for commuting, a backup vehicle, or a project, with straightforward value that\u2019s easy to appreciate.",
